ntent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDD2e6DTTTFzZ_k6DZHLs1Vey-RYw-VX4Vo_pmxZOn4xg&oe=670A59D4"}, "display_name": "ZOSU Castle Morgue Escape", "keywords": [], "long_description": "VR ZOSU Castle Morgue Escape\n- You awaken in a dark and scary abandoned castle that was being used as morgue after a pandemic. It is dark but fortunately you have a flashlight, you must find your way out through a series of simple puzzles and mechanics. \n- This is a casual and somewhat spooky escape-room/area type of game\n- Mostly search and explore with a few cryptic clues to help you along\n- Casually playing it should not take more than 30 minutes\n- Escape the castle quickly for a highscore\n- The last completed round score and highest all time scores are saved\n- Many mysteries, skeletons, and castle areas await you!\n- Some events are slightly randomized for replay ability\n- 3 game modes:\n1) standard in the dark with extra visual hints every few minutes\n2) hard in the dark with no extra timed hints\n3) explore in the light with no puzzles or scoring\n", "short_description": "- You awaken in a dark and scary abandoned castle that was being used as morgue after a pandemic. It is dark but you have a flashlight, you must find your way out through a series of simple puzzles and mechanics. \n- This is a casual and somewhat spooky escape-room/area type of game\n- Escape the castle quickly for a highscore\n- 3 game modes:\n1) standard in the dark with extra visual hints every few minutes\n2) hard in the dark with no extra timed hints\n3) explore in the light with no puzzles or s\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.zosustudio.com/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.zosustudio.com/", "publisher_name": "ZOSU Studios LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.zosustudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"